{"tid":1021041,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"屯門裸女跑落街益街坊 情人節血案：屯門男女赤裸中刀受傷　男子昏迷送院","createTime":"2019-02-14T03:56:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-15T06:33:59.000Z","uid":92376,"like":140,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":53,"replies":[{"pid":"faeec60b48f293c042e678158e77c6a2c4ee3baf","tid":1021041,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T03:56:02.000Z","msg":"屯門發生傷人血案，今早(14日)9時12分，警方接獲一名女子報案，指在青山公路新墟段79至95號竹園大廈走廊，一名年約30歲男子中刀倒臥地上，警員接報趕抵現場，發現一名女子在樓上單位中刀受傷，遂大為緊張，立即封鎖現場，並召救護車將兩名傷者送院，男子送院時陷入昏迷，警方正調查兩人受傷原因，大批探員亦到場搜證。 <br />\n<br />\n據目擊經過的一對鄰居夫婦稱，<span style=\"color: red;\">當時見女事主全身赤裸，走落地下大堂</span>，全身染血，他們遂上前幫忙，惟女事主卻耍手擰頭示意他們「唔好報警」，而男事主則坐於向達仁坊的後門走廊，上身赤膊，下身僅穿着內褲，同樣倒臥血泊。 <br />\n<br />\n啲街坊仲唔大飽眼福？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"720737d9daa011f18b0f9360ac7ae2423c459c66","tid":1021041,"uid":511,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T03:57:20.000Z","msg":"即係個女開個男拖？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/tongue2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55ec9a151108ac2546c5e2cfba2f78d223864dd1","tid":1021041,"uid":92376,"like":5,"dislike":36,"score":-31,"quote":{"pid":"720737d9daa011f18b0f9360ac7ae2423c459c66","tid":1021041,"uid":511,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T03:57:20.000Z","msg":"即係個女開個男拖？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/tongue2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T03:58:50.000Z","msg":"雖然無講條女幾歲<br />\n但正常如果細過條仔 當廿幾<br />\n咁樣赤條條跑落樓真係幾撚養眼<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/tongue2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/tongue2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96b3ea47eff03a77f36f7e701eaf96847cc458dd","tid":1021041,"uid":63909,"like":112,"dislike":2,"score":110,"quote":{"pid":"55ec9a151108ac2546c5e2cfba2f78d223864dd1","tid":1021041,"uid":92376,"like":5,"dislike":36,"score":-31,"quote":{"pid":"720737d9daa011f18b0f9360ac7ae2423c459c66","tid":1021041,"uid":5