rmal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T06:43:04.000Z","msg":"Sor囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 見你咁有誠意 讓返比你"},{"pid":"148dc8cc5ea6abe565620a671633ac12895ae017","tid":1021041,"uid":4811,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"d8f27e7f40c5c31f955e8231bf924c1378c4c1c9","tid":1021041,"uid":117472,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T06:39:52.000Z","msg":"我願意屌鮑姐一個月換一張高清圖"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T06:43:24.000Z","msg":"去街尾排隊啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26a864aa2043f3266930e98932a23d1b1b9d5b3f","tid":1021041,"uid":224561,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T06:52:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190214/59257334\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190214%2F59257334&d=ZfEq%2Fo1sgt4RLlfWMFNbDssFuFiCHHua96MUfZSGoRU%3D&h=8651e9b2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190214%2F59257334&h=9dd5b111\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190214/59257334</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">【14:30】探員展示一把斷成兩截的染血利刀</span><br />\n<br />\n早上9時許，警方接報屯門青山公路新墟段79-95號竹苑有人受傷昏迷。警員趕至現場，發現有一男一女受傷，<span style=\"color: red;\">其中30餘歲的女子身處大廈大堂仍然清醒</span>，但男子則倒在大廈對開10米一處花槽草地，陷入昏迷，救護員相信兩人均中刀受傷，將他們送院救治。<br />\n<br />\n街坊張伯稱，<span style=\"color: red;\">男女傷者都是越南人</span>，較早前搬入1樓劏房單位。事發時他乘電梯落樓，電梯門甫打開，他見到女傷者全身赤裸，坐在保安室內。右面有刀傷，四圍都是血。對方不識講廣東話，未能溝通，張伯連忙報警。稍後他亦見到男傷者在後門位置徘徊，同樣有血，其後不支倒卧花槽。<br />\n<br />\n30餘歲蝻"},{"pid":"0ef259f31844c571d4c0d65c3092a5a8ca31415a","tid":1021041,"uid":184449,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T06:55:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Pf3diOb.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPf3diOb.gif&h=88dcbe6a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"87d7bde7bc41102a6986904b61004cc230c61efd","tid":1021041,"uid":20291,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T06:56:45.000Z","msg":"【14:35】警方相信案件涉及感情糾紛，亦涉及一名男性第三者，該名第三者今早用刀襲擊兩名傷者後逃離現場<br />\n<br />\n應該係兇手係人帽左，番到屋企見到二條肉蟲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dcdbd227e1d5ed24d5f12151a0d17bd17032e06e","tid":1021041,"uid":38465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T07:09:53.000Z","msg":"扑野個陣叫錯名？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6185da7921d9e61953994ae174cb6b7059d9e70","tid":1021041,"uid":161341,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T07:14:48.000Z","msg":"屯門好撚多非法入境者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 由其係小欖果頭"},{"pid":"ed389c6b889d2cf1889babb3c675b5d048220c23","tid":1021041,"uid":33874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"87d7bde7bc41102a6986904b61004cc230c61efd","tid":1021041,"uid":20291,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T06:56:45.000Z","msg":"【14:35】警方相信案件涉及感情糾紛，亦涉及一名男性第三者，該名第三者今早用刀襲擊兩名傷者後逃離現場<br />\n<br />\n應該係兇手係人帽左，番到屋企見到二條肉蟲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T07:17:43.000Z","msg":"巴打做到野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6924f7ac16c931d86069c08ac01d366152cab49e","tid":1021041,"uid":99205,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T08:14:57.000Z","msg":"應該係發現奸夫<br />\n砍得好!!!"},{"pid":"284b187a6855447feee009e30a594ae03298ee8d","tid":1021041,"uid":192078,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f6185da7921d9e61953994ae174cb6b7059d9e70","tid":1021041,"uid":161341,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T07:14:48.000Z","msg":"屯門好撚多非法入境者<img src=\"/asse